_:Na5e5554a550c459cb1a09012eee7ef04 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Journalists with enquiries can contact the <abbr title=\"Department for Science, Innovation &amp; Technology\">DSIT</abbr> press office:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:press@dsit.gov.uk\">press@dsit.gov.uk</a></p>\n\n<p>Phone: 020 7215 3000</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>This phone number and inbox is monitored at all hours.</p>\n\n</div>" .
